<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad von Kochberg, Amtmann zu Coburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Herausgabe der acht Pferde und der Habe von Heinz Hofman und Christian Tiem von Hohenpölz, Armmänner von Hans und Peter Tintner, Bürger zu Nürnberg, und Ledigsagen von der Schatzung.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_63" id="31v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_63_r1l15"><expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> von kochberg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r1l16">Amptman cʒu koburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_63_r1l17">Lıeber Conrad / Vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt Hans vnd peter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r1l18">die Tyntner vnſer Burger / vvie Jr vnd ewr helffer den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r1l19">heincʒen hofman vnd Criſtan Tyemen von hohenpölcʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſeinen </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r1l20">Jren Armenleuten viij pferde / vnd etliche Jr plünder vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r1l24"><expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> h </del> Jr habe genomen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_63_line_1576668695412_2916">vnd ſıe geſacʒt </ab></add> habt / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr den <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r1l25"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> Armenleuten / <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Jre pferde / plunder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r1l27">vnd habe wider ſchicken wöllet 
<add><ab facs="#facs_63_r1l26">vnd ſie vmb dıe <expan>ſchacʒu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> ledıg ſagt </ab></add> / Als etc das wollen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r1l28">vnd lat vns des ewr <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wiſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_63_r1l29"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiij <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Egıdij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_63" id="31v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> von Kochberg, amptman czu Koburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Conrad, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt Hans und Peter
                        die Tyntner, unser burger, wie ir und ewr helffer den Heinczen Hofman und
                        Cristan Tyemen von Hohenpölcz, iren armenleuten, viii pferde und etliche ir
                        plünder und <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan> ir habe genomen <add>und sie
                            gesaczt</add> habt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz ir den
                                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> armenleuten <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        ire pferde, plunder und habe wider schicken wöllet <add>und sie umb die
                                    <expan>schaczu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> ledig sagt</add>, als etc. Das
                        wollen etc. Und lat uns des ewr <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wissen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Egidii.
                    </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
